Aelo::

Aelo was arriving to the place where the battle where, in that way 
that any MAximal Shuttle could see her. She  started scanned and 
Opened her comm link to All Predacons's shuttles.

"Aelo to Predacons" said the femme "Our computers told us that some 
you need help, I need the coordinates... I repeat... I need the 
coordinates."
